\c 2
\s Vanhu vose vanofanira kutongwa
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo imwi hauna manzvengero iwe munhu, upi noupi, unotonga; nokuti pachinhu icho chaunotonga mumwe nacho, unozvipa mhosva iwe, nokuti iwe, unotonga unoita zvinhu zvakangodaro.
\v 2 Asi tinoziva kuti kutonga kwaMwari kunoenderana nechokwadi kunavanoita zvinhu izvozvo.
\v 3 Unofungireiko zvinhu izvi iwe munhu unotonga vanoita zvinhu zvakadai, \add iwe\add* uchiitavo zvakadaro, ungatiza kutonga kwaMwari here?
\v 4 Unozvidza ufumi hwounyoro hwake, nomoyo wake murefu, usingazivi here kuti nyasha dzaMwari dzinokuisa pakutendevuka?
\v 5 Asi novukukutu bwako, nomoyo usingatendevuki, unozvivunganidzira kutsamwa nezuva rokutsamwa, nokuzarurwa kwekutonga kwakarurama kwaMwari;
\v 6 iye uchapa mumwe nomumwe maererano nemabasa ake;
\v 7 kuna ivo nemoyo mirefu vanorambira mumabasa akanaka vachitsvaka kubwinya, nokukudzwa, nokusafa, \add uchavapa\add* upenyu husingaperi.
\v 8 Asi kunavanenharo, vasingateereri chokwadi, asi vanoteerera zvisakarurama, \add kuchavapo\add* kutsamwa nehasha.
\v 9 Kutambudzika nenhamo pamusoro pemweya mumwe nomumwe womunhu unoita zvakaipa, pakutanga womuJudha, nowomuGiriki;
\v 10 asi kubwinya, nokukudzwa, norugare kunomumwe nomumwe unoita zvakanaka, kumuJudha pakutanga, nokumuGirikivo.
\v 11 Nokuti hakuna rusarura gomunhu kunaMwari.
\v 12 Nokuti vose vakatadza pasinomurairo; vachaparadzwavo pasinomurairo; vose vakatadza mumurairo, vachatongwa nomurairo;
\v 13 nokuti havasi vanzwi vomurairo vakarurama pamberi paMwari, asi vaiti vomurairo ndivo vachanzi vakarurama;
\v 14 nokuti kana vahedheni vasinomurairo vachiita pachizvarigo zvinhu zviri mumurairo, ava vasina murairo vachava murairo wavo vamene;
\v 15 vanoratidza basa romurairo wakanyorwa mumoyo yavo, hana yavo ichipupuravo, nemirangariro panguva iyi ichipa mhosva kana kurwira pakati pavo;
\v 16 nezuva iro Mwari paachatonga zvakavanzika zvavanhu, naJesu Kristu, maererano neevhangeri yangu.
\s VaJudha havane-pembedzo
\p
\v 17 Tarira iwe unonzi muJudha, unogutsikana nomurairo, unozvirumbidza munaMwari,
\v 18 unoziva kuda nokutsaura kuti zvakanaka ndezvipi, uchidzidziswa nomurairo,
\v 19 unozvivimba kuti uri mutungamiriri wamapofu, nechiedza chavari murima,
\v 20 nomurairi wamapenzi, nomudzidzisi wavacheche, zvaunomufananidzo woruziva nowechokwadi pamurairo;
\v 21 Naizvozvo iwe unodzidzisa mumwe hauzvidzidzisi here? Iwe unoparidza kuti munhu arege kuba, iwe haubi here?
\v 22 Iwe unoti munhu asaita upombwe, unoita upombwe here? Iwe unosema zvifananidzo, unopamba tembere \add dzavo\add* here?
\v 23 Iwe unozvirumbidza nomurairo, unoshovora Mwari nokudarika murairo here?
\v 24 Nokuti zita raMwari rinomhurwa pakati pavahedheni nokuda kwenyu sezvazvakanyorwa.
\v 25 Nokuti kudzingiswa kunobatsira, kana iwe uchichengeta murairo; asi kana uri mudariki womurairo, kudzingiswa kwako kunoitwa kusadzingiswa.
\v 26 Naizvozvo kana iye usina kudzingiswa achichengeta zviga zvomurairo, ko kusadzingiswa kwake hakunganzi kudzingiswa here?
\v 27 Nousina kudzingiswa kubva pachizvarigo achizadzisa murairo, \add haanga\add*kutongi here iwe unemurairo wakanyorwa nokudzingiswa unodarika murairo?
\v 28 Nokuti haazi muJudha, uri muJudha gokunze; nokudzingiswa hakuzi kokunze kuri panyama;
\v 29 asi iye muJudha ndiye uri \add muJudha\add* nechomukati; nokudzingiswa komoyo mumweya, kwetemumagwaro; kurumbidzwa kwake hakubvi kuvanhu asi kunaMwari.
